name: Jango Fett
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. May deploy Jet Pack on him for free from Reserve Deck; reshuffle; he moves using it for -1 Force. Permanent weapon is Dual Blasters (may lose 1 Force to target a Jedi; until end of turn, choose: target may not fire weapons OR target loses immunity to attrition).(Original concept by Chris Clarke - Australia Nationals 2007)',
